title: Rome 2 total war patch 15+Emperator Edition
description:
This is everything and I mean everything CA has released yet. Possible things to take into account are:
If u dont have the game installed make sure u installed the direct x and all the microsoft redish there are not just the ones that come in the redish folder.
If u had the game already installed make sure you go to you appdata/......rome2 folder and delete everything there for a fresh start.
THe crask has a little flaw which makes the game freeze when exiting so u have to go to control+alt+delete enter the task manager and kill the game.
